Package jacs_player Description

A completely implemented animatronics show player. Will need to be implemented alongside the jmcc package and the jscc package. To utilize the player first create a MicrocontrollerConnection (jmcc package), and then create the PlayerInputs. Next create the FormattedShowData, and create an AnimatronicsShowPlayer. The player can then play, pause, resume, and stop the show, starting and stopping at different times.
